These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-1::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, airplane, car, roller, subway
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: tennis, weightlifting, soccer, badminton, climbing, baseball
 1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
 2. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 3. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person driving the roller and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is the person driving the airplane##1
 6. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
 9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5
10. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
11. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4    |    5     |  6   |
| Transport      | airplane | car   | roller | bus | snowmobile    | subway  |
| Sport   | climbing  | badminton | baseball   | tennis  | weightlifting | soccer |

