.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-2::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, fonseca, dannemann, prince, game, ritmeester
There are 6 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, almond-milk, milk, water, soy-milk
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5
 2. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 3. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 4. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 6. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the dannemann-smoker is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the fonseca-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is the dannemann-smoker##1
10. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
11. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
12. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
13. the game-smoker is the person drinking tea##1
14. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
15. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
16. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |     3      |       4       |     5      |   6    |
| Cigar   | game | ritmeester | dannemann | swisher         | fonseca | prince |
| Beverage   | tea    | water      | almond-milk      | milk | iced-tea   | soy-milk |

