.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-3::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: roller, motorbike, taxi, car, tram, trike
There are 6 different favourite colors: light-blue, chestnut, apricot, ebony, purple, lavender
 1. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 2. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
 3. the person driving the trike is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 5. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
 6. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person who likes light-blue##5
 7. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 9. the person who likes apricot is between the person driving the trike and the person who likes lavender##2
10. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
11. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3    |    4     |    5    |    6     |
| Transport      | trike | roller | tram   | car | motorbike   | taxi |
| Color   | chestnut    | apricot         | lavender | purple     | light-blue | ebony     |

