.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: funk, country, dubstep, folk, hip-hop, soul
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: spy, martial-arts, horror, satire, epic, dubstepsy
 1. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
 2. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 4. the person watching martial-arts movies is the fan of funk##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the fan of soul##5
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
 8. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching dubstepsy movies##3
10. the person watching dubstepsy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
11. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
12. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
13. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4    |       5       |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | country     | dubstep  | soul     | folk | hip-hop |
| Movie-Genre       | martial-arts | dubstepsy | horror | spy | satire          | epic   |

