 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 9. the person drinking cola is the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
12. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
13. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
