.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-19::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  manager, doctor, journalist, accountant, teacher, writer
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: january, april, august, march, june, february
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the writer##3
 2. the teacher is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 3. the manager is on the left of the journalist##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is the teacher##1
 6. the journalist is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the accountant##3
 8. the teacher is in an even position##4
 9. the manager is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
10. the accountant is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the accountant##5
12. the journalist is the person who's birthday is in august##1
13. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the accountant##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5     |       6       |
| Job   | writer  | teacher        | accountant  | manager     | journalist | doctor |
| Birthday       | march | january | february | june | august  | april          |

