.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-20::.
City: london, hannover, venice, paris, colone, rome
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: sunflower, rose, aconite, poppy, amaryllis, tulip
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
 2. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
 3. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 4. the person traveling to hannover is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 5. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
 8. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5
 9. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
10. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
11. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the person who growstulip##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| City         | rome    | paris | hannover   | venice | london    | colone |
| Flower   | sunflower | tulip  | amaryllis | aconite      | poppy | rose    |

 